:     if not summary:\n\n  Line 830:     return summary[:cap]\n\n  Line 848:     The Document's ``data[\"summary\"]`` is populated from the first ~500 chars\n\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 129 matches (29 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":129,"truncated":true},"title":"retrieval_hint|content_preview|summary|slice|brief|citation","time":{"start":1780729443829,"end":1780729443851}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0cb37d476bce1094016a23c663bb648191958eadcfc3414c51"}},"id":"prt_e9bbef5ee0014Y5hkQ5gU0O9XX","sessionID":"ses_164436585ffexoEvsPd4ItVAfq","messageID":"msg_e9bbebf11001QMLECJoOo5qS1t"}}
